Simple smite plugin for Craftbukkit latest RB with a kick!

/smite [playername] - Smites a Player and creates and explosion of a predefind size in config, can be dissabled by setting to zero
/smite - Smites [hits with lighting] and causes and explosion at the block you are looking at, explosion can be set in config the same way as the previous command.

Wewt we hit version 3.0!